  "body": "<p align=\"center\">\n  <a href=\"https://dc.mongenscave.com/\">\n    <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/5191437256bd0575cd6d77ddaed0f8ce92ec09a5.png\" alt=\"Banner\">\n  </a>\n</p>\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <a href=\"https://dc.mongenscave.com/\">\n    <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/ba6b8b13da8eebf0450bfc21cfc52cf4ffb99704.png\" alt=\"Social+\">\n  </a>\n  <a href=\"https://docs.mongenscave.com/free-products/fungun\">\n    <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/eae80f00a73ac68e1e541a75a41ec96f6414b802_0.webp\" alt=\"Docs\">\n  </a>\n</p>\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <a href=\"https://dc.mongenscave.com/\">\n    <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/BjEHc5p.gif\" alt=\"Effect GUI\">\n  </a>\n</p>\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <a href=\"https://dc.mongenscave.com/\">\n    <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/i7s0vyk.gif\" alt=\"Ability GUI\">\n  </a>\n</p>\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <a href=\"https://dc.mongenscave.com/\">\n    <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/48918c32c2b7302445aec9ad4fd1983a59330421.png\" alt=\"Folia\">\n  </a>\n</p>\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <a href=\"https://dc.mongenscave.com/\">\n    <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/fecc2039d34d199fcbbebf5dbc9ddc360e6dcd0f.png\" alt=\"Database\">\n  </a>\n</p>\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <a href=\"https://dc.mongenscave.com/\">\n    <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/b1bfe71c0f85498d7ad904200826fb9a72cafce2.png\" alt=\"Feature 1\">\n  </a>\n</p>\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <a href=\"https://dc.mongenscave.com/\">\n    <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/dee71a68d8054362e0d8e85bfb3750be22411652.png\" alt=\"Feature 2\">\n  </a>\n</p>\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <a href=\"https://dc.mongenscave.com/\">\n    <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/5462510af4e0928f634b3ea46d693b1f91be31c3.png\" alt=\"Feature 3\">\n  </a>\n</p>\n\n\n<details>\n<summary>Text Transcript</summary>\nFunGun\nInject a new vibe into your lobby servers and create a cheerful atmosphere!\n\nFREE Discord Support | Full Documented Plugin\n\nFeatures:\n- Fully Customizable GUIS, Messages and Config\n- Fully Customizable FunGun Item\n- Toggleable effects, abilitys\n- Toggleable the ability function\n- Custom Model Data Support\n- HEX Color code Support\n- Folia Support\n- You can create your own effect\n- Give Command\n- Database Support: MySQL, H2 & SQLite\n- Version Support: 1.21.x - 1.18\n\nMajor Features:\n- FunGun Effects:\nUse over 30 unique effects with FunGun! Simply right-click with the item to launch a snowball that leaves a stunning visual effect upon landing.\n\n- FunGun Abilities:\nGive your Lobby server a fresh vibe and build anticipation with FunGun’s abilities! Choose from pre-made abilities or create your own!\n\n- Multiple Server Support:\nSave FunGun settings to a MySQL database for flexible use across multiple Lobby servers simultaneously.\n</details>\n\n",
